<doc id="52841665" url="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=52841665" title="Thermophyte">
Thermophyte

Thermophyte (Greek "thérmos" = warmth, heat + "phyton" = plant) is a plant which is tolerant or thriving at high temperatures. These plants are categorized according to ecological valences at high temperatures, including biological extremely. Such plants included the hot-spring taxa also.
